<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23398718-the-man-who-wasn-t-there"><img alt="The Man Who Wasn&#39;t There: Investigations into the Strange New Science of the Self" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1417983505l/23398718._SX98_.jpg" />
